{
  "sourceLanguage" : "en",
  "strings" : {
    "\"%@\" (%@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%@" : {
      "comment" : "Informative text in an NSAlert confirmation dialog for first-time authorization of the Settings URI handler. The first argument is the app name. The second argument is the bundle identifier. The third argument is the string “”, the string “\n\nSigned by: %arg”, or the string “\n\n⚠️ Warning: This app is not code-signed.”.",
      "localizations" : {
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„%1$@“ (%2$@) žádá o povolení ovládat nastavení aplikace Thaw prostřednictvím URL schématu.\n\nPokud bude povoleno, bude tato aplikace moci:\n• Číst aktuální nastavení a konfigurace\n• Přepínat logické volby\n• Upravovat číselné hodnoty (časovače, zpoždění, intervaly)\n• Měnit nastavení výběrových typů (způsoby opětovného skrytí, umístění lišty Thaw)\n• Upravovat konfigurace pro jednotlivé obrazovky\n\nToto oprávnění zůstává platné, dokud aplikaci ručně neodstraníte v nastavení Thaw → Automatizace.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) will Thaw-Einstellungen über das URL-Schema steuern.\n\nWenn erlaubt, wird diese Anwendung in der Lage sein folgendes zu tun:\n• aktuelle Einstellungen und Konfigurationen\nlesen\n• booleschen Einstellungen umschalten und ändern\n• numerische Werte ändern (Timer, Verzögerungen, Intervalle)\n• Einstellungen ändern (Versteck-Strategie, Ort der Thaw-Leiste)\n• modifizieren der Konfigurationen pro Anzeige\n\nDiese Berechtigung bleibt bestehen, bis sie manuel unter Einstellungen > Automatisierung entfernt wird.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) desea controlar los ajustes de Thaw mediante un esquema de URL.\n\nSi se permite, esta aplicación podrá:\n• Leer los ajustes y configuraciones actuales\n• Activar y desactivar ajustes booleanos\n• Modificar valores numéricos (temporizadores, retrasos, intervalos)\n• Cambiar ajustes de menú (estrategia de ocultación, ubicación de la barra de Thaw)\n• Modificar configuraciones para cada pantalla\n\nEste permiso permanecerá activo hasta que se elimine manualmente en Ajustes > Automatización.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) ingin mengontrol pengaturan Thaw melalui skema URL.\n\nJika dizinkan, aplikasi ini dapat:\n• Membaca pengaturan dan konfigurasi saat ini\n• Mengaktifkan atau menonaktifkan pengaturan boolean\n• Mengubah nilai numerik (waktu, jeda, interval)\n• Mengubah pengaturan enum (strategi sembunyi-ulang, lokasi Bar Thaw)\n• Mengubah konfigurasi per layar\n\nIzin ini akan tetap berlaku hingga dihapus secara manual di Pengaturan > Otomatisasi.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%1$@」（%2$@）が、URL スキームを通じて Thaw の設定を制御しようとしています。\n\n許可すると、このアプリは以下の操作が可能になります：\n• 現在の設定および構成の読み取り\n• ブール値設定の切り替えおよび変更\n• 数値の変更（タイマー、遅延、間隔など）\n• 列挙型設定の変更（再非表示の方式、Thaw Bar の位置）\n• ディスプレイごとの設定の変更\n\nこの権限は、「設定 > 自動化」で手動で削除されるまで有効です。%3$@"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) chce kontrolować ustawienia Thaw za pomocą schematu URL.\n\nJeśli wyrazisz zgodę, ta aplikacja będzie mogła:\n• Odczytywać bieżące parametry i konfiguracje\n• Przełączać i zmieniać ustawienia włącz/wyłącz\n• Modyfikować wartości liczbowe (liczniki, opóźnienia, interwały)\n• Zmieniać ustawienia typu enum (strategię ponownego ukrywania, położenie paska Thaw)\n• Modyfikować konfiguracje dla poszczególnych wyświetlaczy\n\nTo uprawnienie pozostanie aktywne do momentu jego ręcznego cofnięcia w sekcji Ustawienia > Automatyzacja.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“%1$@” (%2$@), URL şeması aracılığıyla Thaw ayarlarını kontrol etmek istiyor.\n\nİzin verilirse, bu uygulama aşağıdakileri yapabilir:\n• Mevcut ayarları ve yapılandırmaları okuyabilir\n• Mantıksal ayarları açıp kapatabilir ve değiştirebilir\n• Sayısal değerleri (zamanlayıcılar, bekleme süreleri, zaman aralıkları) değiştirebilir\n• Liste ayarlarını (yeniden gizleme stratejisi, Thaw Bar konumu) değiştirebilir\n• Her ekran için yapılandırmaları değiştirebilir\n\nBu izin, Ayarlar > Otomasyon'da el ile kaldırılana kadar geçerli kalır.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) muốn kiểm soát cài đặt Thaw thông qua lược đồ URL.\n\nNếu được phép, ứng dụng này sẽ có thể:\n• Đọc các cài đặt và cấu hình hiện tại\n• Chuyển đổi và thay đổi cài đặt boolean\n• Sửa đổi các giá trị số (bộ tính giờ, độ trễ, khoảng thời gian)\n• Thay đổi cài đặt enum (ẩn lại chiến lược, vị trí thanh Thaw)\n• Sửa đổi cấu hình trên mỗi màn hình\n\nQuyền này vẫn tồn tại cho đến khi bị xóa thủ công trong Cài đặt > Tự động hóa.%3$@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) 希望通过 URL Scheme 控制 Thaw 的设置。\n\n如果允许，该应用将能够：\n• 读取当前设置与配置\n• 切换和修改布尔类型设置\n• 修改数值参数（计时器、延迟、间隔等）\n• 更改枚举类型设置（如重新隐藏策略、Thaw Bar 位置）\n• 修改各显示器的独立配置\n\n此权限将持续生效，直到在 设置 > 自动化 中手动移除。%3$@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "\"%1$@\" (%2$@) wants to control Thaw settings via URL scheme.\n\nIf allowed, this app will be able to:\n• Read current settings and configurations\n• Toggle and change boolean settings\n• Modify numeric values (timers, delays, intervals)\n• Change enum settings (rehide strategy, Thaw Bar location)\n• Modify per-display configurations\n\nThis permission persists until manually removed in Settings > Automation.%3$@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
