    "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions." : {
      "comment" : "A tooltip that explains the purpose of a setting.",
      "localizations" : {
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Po přepnutí profilů se ikony v řádku nabídek na displejích s výřezem seřadí pomocí rychlejší metody LCS („nejdelší společná posloupnost“) namísto úplného přeřazení. Metoda LCS sníží počet přesunů, ale na displejích s výřezem a nižším rozlišením může být méně spolehlivá."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Den schnelleren LCS-Algoritmus (Longest Common Subsequence) für die Profilsortierung anstatt der vollständigen Sortierung auf Bildschirmen mit Notch nutzen. LCS minimiert die Anzahl der Bewegungen kann aber auf Bildschirmen mit Notch mit geringeren Auflösungen weniger zuverlässig sein."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Utilice el algoritmo LCS más rápido (una secuencia común más larga) para ordenar perfiles en pantallas marcadas en lugar del tipo completo. LCS minimiza el número de movimientos, pero puede ser menos fiable en pantallas con resoluciones más pequeñas."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Gunakan algoritma LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) yang lebih cepat untuk mengurutkan profil pada layar notch sebagai pengganti algoritma bawaan. LCS mengurangi jumlah perpindahan, tetapi mungkin kurang optimal di layar notch beresolusi kecil."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ノッチ付きディスプレイでのプロファイル並び替えにおいて、完全ソートの代わりに高速な LCS（最長共通部分列）アルゴリズムを使用します。LCS は移動回数を最小限に抑えますが、解像度の低いノッチ付きディスプレイでは精度が低下する場合があります。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Używaj szybszego algorytmu LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) do sortowania profili na wyświetlaczach z notchem zamiast pełnego sortowania. LCS minimalizuje liczbę przesunięć, ale może być mniej niezawodny na ekranach z notchem o niższej rozdzielczości."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Используйте более быстрый алгоритм LCS (Наибольшей общей подпоследовательности) для сортировки профилей на дисплеях с вырезом. LCS минимизирует кол-во перемещений, но может быть менее надежным на экранах с вырезом и низким разрешением."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sử dụng thuật toán LCS (Chuỗi tiếp theo chung dài nhất) nhanh hơn để sắp xếp cấu hình trên màn hình có khía thay vì sắp xếp đầy đủ. LCS giảm thiểu số lần di chuyển nhưng có thể kém tin cậy hơn trên màn hình có khía có độ phân giải nhỏ hơn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在刘海屏设备上，对配置排序时使用更快的 LCS（最长公共子序列）算法，而不是完整排序。LCS 可减少元素移动次数，但在分辨率较低的刘海屏设备上可能稳定性较差。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Use the faster LCS (Longest Common Subsequence) algorithm for profile sorting on notched displays instead of the full sort. LCS minimises the number of moves but may be less reliable on notched displays with smaller resolutions."
          }
        }
      }
    },
